{
  "texts": [
    "For example, cultural connection and ACTFL standards being integrated into teacher input were largely restricted to the outputs generated by P.5.",
    "Warm-up serving to activate prior knowledge and integration of the ACTFL standards into the focus and review were largely restricted to groups P.1 and P.2.",
    "Teacher input engaging learners in interaction was restricted largely to P.1, P.2, and P.5.",
    "In all of these examples of heterogeneity between prompt outputs, the appearance of rubric elements was often restricted to only around 50% of the outputs, indicating non-determinism in generated responses.",
